 Write a program to sort a String alphabetically.

Here's the program in Java that sorts a string alphabetically:

import java.util.Arrays;

public class StringSortExample {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String input = "Hello world";

        // Convert the string to a character array
        char[] chars = input.toCharArray();

        // Sort the character array in ascending order
        Arrays.sort(chars);

        // Create a new string from the sorted character array
        String sortedString = new String(chars);

        System.out.println("Original string: " + input);
        System.out.println("Sorted string: " + sortedString);
    }
}

